snippet.title: Open Beta Live Now | Gameplay Trailer | Indus Battle Royale
snippet.description:
The most anticipated mobile game of India- Indus Battle Royale is now officially in OPEN BETA!

Test Indus Battle Royale on iOS: https://testflight.apple.com/join/f6DSKbbq
Test Open Beta on Android: https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.indusgame.play

Change the game with Cosmium Clutch- our unique winning feature and conquer in unwinnable scenarios.
Got eliminated in Virlok? No need to rage. Get back at your nemesis by declaring a GRUDGE- our revenge feature & a first in any Battle Royale. 
The revolution is on its way and we’re here to stay. See you on Virlok!

Track Credits:

Performed by:
Quest (IG: @ayo.quest)
Aneesha Dass (IG: @aneesha.d)

Produced by:
Chaitanya Bhalla (IG: @chazz.guitar)

To catch all the updates about Indus, Follow us on:
Discord: https://discord.gg/indusgame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/indusgame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/IndusGame
WhatsApp: https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029VaKa2jZ2Jl8C1ZInNq1U
Website: https://www.indusgame.com



#indusbattleroyale #battleroyale #gaming #indusopenbeta
